	<content_vi_html>&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;M&amp;ocirc; tả c&amp;ocirc;ng việc&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Thực hiện follow, khai th&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng chiến lược được giao;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Hỗ trợ Demo, tư vấn cho kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng về c&amp;aacute;c sản phẩm, giải ph&amp;aacute;p phần mềm;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Đ&amp;agrave;m ph&amp;aacute;n, thực hiện hồ sơ, hợp đồng, đấu thầu;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Theo d&amp;otilde;i t&amp;igrave;nh h&amp;igrave;nh triển khai phần mềm, duy tr&amp;igrave; chăm s&amp;oacute;c kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng, theo d&amp;otilde;i thanh quyết to&amp;aacute;n hợp đồng;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Phối hợp với c&amp;aacute;c bộ phận, ph&amp;ograve;ng ban thực hiện c&amp;ocirc;ng việc kinh doanh;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;a style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;Phối hợp, l&amp;agrave;m việc với H&amp;atilde;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng nghệ tư vấn giải ph&amp;aacute;p phần mềm&lt;/a&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- L&amp;ecirc;n kế hoạch v&amp;agrave; thực hiện c&amp;ocirc;ng việc theo đ&amp;uacute;ng mục ti&amp;ecirc;u cam kết.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Y&amp;ecirc;u cầu:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;Tốt nghiệp ĐH CNTT, T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng, Kinh tế, Ngoại thương, Ngoại giao;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Y&amp;ecirc;u th&amp;iacute;ch c&amp;ocirc;ng việc quan hệ kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng, ngoại giao, kinh doanh, CNTT;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Đ&amp;atilde; l&amp;agrave;m sale trong CNTT &amp;ndash; phần mềm từ 2 năm trở l&amp;ecirc;n hoặc sale trong Ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Đ&amp;atilde; l&amp;agrave;m sale/sale support trong c&amp;aacute;c H&amp;atilde;ng c&amp;ocirc;ng nghệ nước ngo&amp;agrave;i tại VN;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- C&amp;oacute; base về CNTT hoặc T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Đặc biệt ưu tiền sale đ&amp;atilde;/đang tham gia c&amp;aacute;c dự &amp;aacute;n phần mềm cho Ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng, t&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh, ch&amp;iacute;nh phủ;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- T&amp;iacute;nh chủ động cao, nhiệt huyết, năng động trong suy nghĩ;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Tiếng Anh giao tiếp tốt + đọc hiểu t&amp;agrave;i liệu.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quyền lợi:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;a style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;/a&gt;Thu nhập rất cạnh tranh;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Thưởng kinh doanh hấp dẫn;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Cơ chế cổ phần ưu đ&amp;atilde;i;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- C&amp;aacute;c chế độ bảo hiểm theo Luật lao động + bảo hiểm ưu đ&amp;atilde;i;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- Teambuilding, nghỉ h&amp;egrave; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c ph&amp;uacute;c lợi kh&amp;aacute;c;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- L&amp;agrave;m việc với team kinh nghiệm chuy&amp;ecirc;n s&amp;acirc;u về T&amp;agrave;i ch&amp;iacute;nh ng&amp;acirc;n h&amp;agrave;ng, c&amp;ocirc;ng nghệ;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;- M&amp;ocirc;i trường cởi mở, hấp dẫn, thời gian linh hoạt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ứng vi&amp;ecirc;n quan t&amp;acirc;m vui l&amp;ograve;ng gửi CV về DTSVN: vietla@dtsvn.net&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ffffff;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hotline: 0345539193&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content_vi_html>
	<content_en_html>&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="text-align: justify;"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perform follow-up and develop assigned strategic customers;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support demo sessions, provide consulting for customers on software products and solutions;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Negotiate, prepare documents, contracts, and participate in bidding processes;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Monitor software implementation, maintain customer care, and follow up on contract settlement;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Coordinate with departments and teams to carry out business activities;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborate and work with technology vendors to provide software solutions;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop plans and execute tasks according to committed objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="text-align: justify;"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bachelor&amp;rsquo;s degree in IT, Finance &amp;amp; Banking, Economics, International Trade, or International Relations;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Passion for customer relations, diplomacy, business, and IT;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At least 2 years of sales experience in IT/software or sales in the banking industry;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience in sales/sales support at international technology companies in Vietnam;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Background in IT or Finance &amp;amp; Banking;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strongly preferred: sales professionals who have participated in software projects for banking, finance, or government sectors;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Highly proactive, enthusiastic, and dynamic mindset;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good English communication skills + ability to read and understand documents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="text-align: justify;"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Highly competitive income;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Attractive sales incentives;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Preferential stock options;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Insurance according to labor law + additional benefits;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Teambuilding, summer vacation, and other perks;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work with an experienced team specializing in Finance, Banking, and Technology;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Open, engaging work environment with flexible working hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to Apply&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Interested candidates please send your CV to DTSVN: &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a&gt;vietla@dtsvn.net&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hotline: &lt;strong&gt;0345539193&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content_en_html>
